was first-- she first tasted it

00:34:24.280 --> 00:34:26.620 align:middle line:90%
60 years before.

00:34:26.620 --> 00:34:29.719 align:middle line:90%
Then you have snifters.

00:34:29.719 --> 00:34:31.710 align:middle line:84%
All of us are combinations,
but most of us

00:34:31.710 --> 00:34:34.070 align:middle line:90%
have one or two dominants.

00:34:34.070 --> 00:34:38.040 align:middle line:84%
Like mine is audio
and kinesthetic.

