Yes.

00:43:11.110 --> 00:43:13.260 align:middle line:84%
Always sends chills
through my whole body.

00:43:13.260 --> 00:43:14.170 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:43:14.170 --> 00:43:19.458 align:middle line:84%
>>HOUSTON: I want you to hear
