00:43:36.260 --> 00:43:37.650 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:43:37.650 --> 00:43:41.840 align:middle line:84%
I-- My whole body is so
completely energized.

00:43:41.840 --> 00:43:42.940 align:middle line:90%
My hands are hot.

00:43:42.940 --> 00:43:44.780 align:middle line:90%
Look, flushed.

00:43:44.780 --> 00:43:45.860 align:middle line:90%
Look.

00:43:45.860 --> 00:43:46.776 align:middle line:90%
>>HOUSTON: Absolutely.

00:43:46.776 --> 00:43:48.350 align:middle line:90%
Whoa, yes.

00:43:48.350 --> 00:43:51.410 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Because my
entire body is engaged.

00:43:51.410 --> 00:43:54.620 align:middle line:84%
And towards-- and when
you move your every cell

00:43:54.620 --> 00:43:57.890 align:middle line:84%
of your body towards
that goal, whatever

00:43:57.890 --> 00:44:02.980 align:middle line:84%
it is for other people, you
feel that entire-- that happens.

00:44:02.980 --> 00:44:04.270 align:middle line:90%
That absolutely happens.

00:44:04.270 --> 00:44:06.186 align:middle line:84%
>>HOUSTON: Because that's
one of the best ways

00:44:06.186 --> 00:44:09.720 align:middle line:84%
to activate these
interior images.

00:44:09.720 --> 00:44:11.680 align:middle line:84%
Now when you activate
interior images,

00:44:11.680 --> 00:44:14.700 align:middle line:84%
you will find that you can
become much more creative

00:44:14.700 --> 00:44:17.140 align:middle line:84%
because you're thinking
in images not in words.

00:44:17.140 --> 00:44:21.280 align:middle line:84%
And what happens is that the
mind can select, synthesize,

00:44:21.280 --> 00:44:22.910 align:middle line:84%
do the work of
months in minutes,

00:44:22.910 --> 00:44:24.160 align:middle line:90%
as we find in high creativity.

00:44:24.160 --> 00:44:25.159 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh, that's nice.

00:44:25.159 --> 00:44:25.790 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

